SPEAKER: Yes.

00:22:13.560 --> 00:22:16.490
Quentin, what's it like to
be back on stage with Kenita?

00:22:16.490 --> 00:22:17.730
Is it-- after so many years--

00:22:17.730 --> 00:22:18.860
QUENTIN EARL DARRINGTON:
Oh, it's everything.

00:22:18.860 --> 00:22:19.526
It's everything.

00:22:19.526 --> 00:22:22.040
I actually told my
cast the first day

00:22:22.040 --> 00:22:23.180
of one of our workshops--

00:22:23.180 --> 00:22:25.100
I walked in the
room, and they asked,

00:22:25.100 --> 00:22:27.350
so what is the most
exciting part about today?

00:22:27.350 --> 00:22:29.220
Michael Arden asked
us all to say what's

00:22:29.220 --> 00:22:30.470
your most exciting part today?

00:22:30.470 --> 00:22:32.220
And think of something
you may be the most

00:22:32.220 --> 00:22:33.460
trepidatious about today.

00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:35.630
And I said, the most
exciting thing about today

00:22:35.630 --> 00:22:38.660
is that I get to work
with and hear and see

00:22:38.660 --> 00:22:42.060
my favorite singer on Broadway.

00:22:42.060 --> 00:22:44.030
And it's Kenita.

00:22:44.030 --> 00:22:46.020
From day one-- I've
known Kenita now

00:22:46.020 --> 00:22:49.850
since 2001 when we
started "Ragtime" together

00:22:49.850 --> 00:22:51.710
with Lynn and Stephen.

00:22:51.710 --> 00:22:53.670
So it's been a long time.

00:22:53.670 --> 00:22:57.740
And she's been my friend ever
since, and met her husband

00:22:57.740 --> 00:23:01.080
the same tour, the
same show, back then.

00:23:01.080 --> 00:23:03.170
So I've known the both of
them this whole journey.

00:23:03.170 --> 00:23:04.890
So it truly is family, man.

00:23:04.890 --> 00:23:07.610
It's the coolest
thing in the world.

00:23:07.610 --> 00:23:08.370
It's awesome.

00:23:08.370 --> 00:23:09.369
SPEAKER: That's awesome.

00:23:09.369 --> 00:23:11.780
Miss Loren, can we talk?

00:23:11.780 --> 00:23:12.850
LOREN LOTT: We can talk.

00:23:12.850 --> 00:23:14.599
SPEAKER: You know, I
feel like Joan Rivers

00:23:14.599 --> 00:23:15.584
up here or something.

