[LAUGHTER]

00:23:18.320 --> 00:23:21.374
So first of all, that
performance-- just,

00:23:21.374 --> 00:23:22.790
please, another
round of applause.

00:23:22.790 --> 00:23:23.557
That was--

00:23:23.557 --> 00:23:26.239
[APPLAUSE]

00:23:26.239 --> 00:23:29.210
Just blown away completely.

