And actually, the night
that I was seeing the show,

00:23:32.540 --> 00:23:34.796
we saw it with you as Ti Moune.

00:23:34.796 --> 00:23:35.420
LOREN LOTT: Oh.

00:23:35.420 --> 00:23:36.790
SPEAKER: Yes.

00:23:36.790 --> 00:23:38.081
LOREN LOTT: I didn't know that.

00:23:38.081 --> 00:23:41.030
You didn't tell me
that this whole time?

00:23:41.030 --> 00:23:43.220
SPEAKER: I was like, oh my God.

